Class MissingMatrixVariableException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception

              • org.springframework.web.bind.MissingRequestValueException
                • org.springframework.web.bind.MissingMatrixVariableException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MissingMatrixVariableException
extends MissingRequestValueException
    ServletRequestBindingException subclass that indicates that a matrix variable expected in the method parameters of an @RequestMapping method is not present among the matrix variables extracted from the URL.
    Since:
    5.1
    Author:
    Juergen Hoeller
    See Also:
    MissingPathVariableException, Serialized Form
